Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美丽的环境是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.71,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 买了什么回来啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八话  爱玩（珍惜、爱护）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…是雪貂 好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我经常去的宠物店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,优惠价卖给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到这可爱的脸就舍不得放开它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样 是不是跟阿薰有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟薰…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 你对它有什么打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事就要拜托房东…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 这样可以逗它玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,养它没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样小葵也陷下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是雅会怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  准  养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管…管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 我还在想怎么这么吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是把这种东西带了进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还打算把它养在这里 你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上宠物这种东西会弄脏房间 又会产生气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好的考虑一下后果行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道吗？我身为这栋房子的管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有保护这里的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.07,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痒死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在立刻把它还回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何都不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它明明这么可爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 要是养了这个动物的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会给水无月添麻烦的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要养它吗？好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 随你们高兴好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是这跟我没有任何的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定了的话 首先是住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？很帅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就算只有一只在里面睡也不会寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驳回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 你要做什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弄得这么朴素 太可怜了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事情简单朴素就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我就来给它铺软软的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱…抱歉 这是我的内衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多这样可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有点太烫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 在喝了在喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害的吃像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 喝得津津有味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多喝一点 然后健康的长大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来小葵有孩子后会变成一个好妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.87,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看你看 很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锵…钓雪貂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 名字要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有什么好的意见呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有什么比较帅的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅你有什么意见吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这跟我没有任何的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是吵闹的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.39,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 根本就不是让心情平静的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动物这种东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂…娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.78,0:07:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么啊？蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它又不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它？那只雪貂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 要是再让管理员讨厌就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 阿薰也来帮我找好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅 要不要喝点茶呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确是放在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅 发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 葵大小姐 不是什么重要的事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放在这是的我的钢笔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢笔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惨了 是管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来不及了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你！给我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水无月 抓住它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 抓错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 那里不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.67,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 罐子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 在这里 给我下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…这是我的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有办法再容忍下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员真是好可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 看起来已经完完全全生气了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系的 雅一定会让我们养它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我站住！喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于放弃了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经逃不掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难…难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！不要来这边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蟑螂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那是我的扣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直在找的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扣子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅 没关系的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是蟑螂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把扣子当蟑螂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到管理员也会有不知所措的一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到雅也有克星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.63,0:11:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是意外耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思这样笑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没恶意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对对 因为实在是太意外了 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次是真的火大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在只能先等她气消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就可以吃午餐了 你要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都在等喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是一样不出声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肚子也饿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也明白吗？吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快点来到话菜要冷掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 真不肯放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我是不是也太小孩子气了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么声音…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在干什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.75,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起来它也在为雅担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是打算等雅出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我管理员的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是会危害到这房子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算只是只宠物也不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不想想到底是因为谁才会变成这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.73,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上就整理干净 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧吗？妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉真不对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙做事出错之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不和管理员的斥责接起来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜都冷掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它也没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.57,0:14:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 为什么那只雪貂这么在意管理员呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明老是被追打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不打算吃东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许它是打算等到雅出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它也和雅一样饿着肚子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就把饭菜端到管理员的房间去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再拜托一次雪貂的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来只要签名…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢笔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不用那只钢笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的笔也能用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算放弃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直『卡哩卡哩』地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会在这种地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被夹住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂！雪貂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我马上把你弄出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜不行 它会痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里实在是太窄 没办法拉出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办 怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能把这个移开的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动都不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也来帮忙 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大家一起帮忙 也许能够搬得动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油…马上就会救你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.72,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂不动了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能放弃啊 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算这样说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会死掉的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂它不动了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.88,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家再加油试一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一、二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,东西坏了 只要再修就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够替代的东西要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.77,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有生命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍一下 只要再忍耐一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅！薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅 不要紧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失…失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪貂…太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.07,0:19:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 就是这样我才讨厌动物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅也从房间里出来了 真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是托它的福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的名字就取作『钿女』吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女…是那个日本神话的？
